{"tid":2370071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Win 10一句指令可使硬碟損壞  或無法完全修復","createTime":"2021-01-17T17:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T07:16:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf158234359132c5ec5c11f5f51884b02172ea5a","tid":2370071,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"雖然之前 Windows 10 亦出現過不少 Bug，不過多數影響小部分用戶。近日外國研究人員發現一個 Windows 10 Bug，只需使用一句短字串指令便可令用戶硬碟損壞，而從文中測試影片看來，似乎沒辦法完全修復。而最危險的是這個 Bug 似乎<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>對所有 Windows 10 電腦都有影響</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/command.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fcommand.jpg&h=299a7536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n近日外國網站 Bleeping Computer 發佈文章並指出他們發現的一個 Windows 10 Bug。根據文章指出，只需一句簡單的短字串指令，使能夠破壞使用者 NTFS 格式硬碟。而且這個指令還可以使用多種方式來引導使用者觸發，例如偽裝成 ZIP、HTML 文件甚至是其他文件格式等。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1-2-694x580.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F1-2-694x580.png&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=50677fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1-2-694x580.png</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/17/windows-10-reproduces-bugs-and-damages-users-hard-drives/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F17%2Fwindows-10-reproduces-bugs-and-damages-users-hard-drives%2Flife-tech%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=c784ed0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/17/windows-10-reproduces-bugs-and-damages-users-hard-drives/life-tech/</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n而從文章中的測試影片看來，似乎沒辦法完全修復。只要輸入該短字串指令後，雖然會顯示無法找到。但過了幾秒鐘之後，就會跳出需要重新啟動修復硬碟錯誤，並且要求現在重新開機。接著便會進入修復畫面，修復完後重新開機會再度出現錯誤，然後再次進行修復硬碟錯誤。而 Windows 10 事件日誌也出現錯誤報告。"},{"pid":"c43fbee093eae79cec0de2c82921f29cff065ec4","tid":2370071,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf3d978888562f21204df3c90b1192258483749","tid":2370071,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1-2-694x580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F1-2-694x580.png&h=8cf9d3cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c188a61d092c358049bd82f70ae684fc5f429a6","tid":2370071,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"N年前既硬碟清除txt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f988117620de3a6d70073d7016b166b3ddb61db3","tid":2370071,"uid":16528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"484b152fd9ead3a6c6231911be9b02902107cb3b","tid":2370071,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"old news is so 唔識串，老貓鍾意考古<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba94b8bd61d0b225ff2ca19036c43e714d2e7ad","tid":2370071,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"c: format c：/s"},{"pid":"40fb038a86e512e60999e0997da8c6830d0e168c","tid":2370071,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0